X-WR-CALNAME:Windrush line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-01T22:30:00&endDate=2026-04-02T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 30\, Tuesday 31 March\, Wednesday 1 and Thursday 2 April\, after 2330 each evening\, no service between New Cross Gate and West Croydon / Crystal Palace. Rail replacement buses will run as follows: the bus for Streatham Hill via Crystal Palace will depart London Bridge at 2358 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Crystal Palace\, Gipsy Hill\, West Norwood\, Tulse Hill and Streatham Hill. \r\n\r\nThe bus for East Croydon will depart London Bridge at 0035 calling at New Cross Gate\, Brockley\, Honor Oak Park\, Forest Hill\, Sydenham\, Norwood Junction and East Croydon. One return bus from Crystal Palace departs at 2359\, calling at all stations to London Bridge via New Cross Gate. Alternatively\, use local buses or trams via any reasonable route. \r\n\r\nLast through trains: New Cross Gate to Crystal Palace 2324\, Crystal Palace to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2332\; New Cross Gate to West Croydon 2330\, West Croydon to New Cross Gate / Highbury & Islington 2316. The 2232 and 2247 Highbury & Islington to West Croydon trains are diverted to Crystal Palace and the 2338 Dalston Junction to New Cross Gate train does not run.
DTEND:20260402T002900Z
DTSTART:20260401T223000Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Special Service
UID:4b8a38a2-d89f-4324-8d55-c157d84808d6@4b8a.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-21T22:15:00&endDate=2026-04-22T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Tuesday 21 and Wednesday 22 April\, after 2315 each evening\, no service between Surrey Quays and Clapham Junction / Battersea Park. Use local bus route 35 (for Denmark Hill\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; bus route 37 (for Peckham Rye\, Brixton\, Clapham High Street and Clapham Junction)\; and bus route 381 (for Surrey Quays\, South Bermondsey\, Queens Road Peckham and Peckham Rye). For Wandsworth Road\, use Clapham High Street\, which is a short walk away. Last through trains: Surrey Quays to Clapham Junction 2307 (Departs Dalston Junction at 2249)\; Clapham Junction to Dalston Junction 2315
DTEND:20260422T002900Z
DTSTART:20260421T221500Z
SUMMARY:Windrush line: Part Closure
